SENANDUNG ARSITEKTUR
experiencing emotions through atmosphere 
A project which comprises installation exhibit, performing arts, and music performances.

Get ready to experience emotions through atmosphere! See you there!

THE LONG AWAITED TIME HAS COME!
.
I, Michelle Hutauruk support Stefanny to be the President of HMJ Ilmu Komunikasi 2017/2018 .
Don't forget to cast your vote as a privellege from being a Communication Student
.
The election will be held for two days only, so better make it count! You can cast your vote on:
Date: - Tuesday 30th of May 2017 or - Wednesday 31st of May 2017 
Time: 9am - 2pm 
Place: Building F, 9th Floor
Do bring your smartcard to vote!
.
Make sure to participate because your vote determines the future of HMJ Ilmu Komunikasi UPH!

I, Michelle Hutauruk, can't wait to see you in One Communication 2016!

One Communication is a perfect moment for Ilkomers batch 2016 & also seniors to spend some time together. It will be held on 21st to 23rd of October 2016 in UPH & Tania Adventure, Bandung. -
For 3 days, we can learn more about our major & get to know each other in the most fun way possible! You will also be officially claimed as a Communication student in a very special ceremony! But...is that it?
-
